<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6223c5a0-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s318"><num value="318">§ 318.</num><heading> Amendment or repeal of sections</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Congress reserves the right at any time to alter, amend, or repeal sections 312 to 318 of this title or any portion thereof.</p>
